name: Say YES to the Void
description: Why deny it give yourself over to the abyss. Early VHS Text Art piece by Sarah Zucker, 2017. Hi8 Camcorder Title Feedback and digital animation with analog glitch processing on VHS. Filmed in 1080p from vintage CRT TV Screen. Purchase unlocks access to hi-res loopable .mp4.
